did.abstract: This collection contains issues of The Zamboni, a student-run journal of humor at Tufts, and web crawls documenting its web presence.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: This collection is organized into two series: The Zamboni and Web crawls.

custodhist.head: Custodial History
custodhist.p: These publications are picked up by DCA staff when they can get them.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This collection contains issues of The Zamboni, a student-run journal of humor at Tufts, and web crawls documenting its web presence. It includes annual issues from 1992 through 2001, and more frequent issues since 2001.

processinfo.head: Processing status
processinfo.p: This collection is processed and open for research.
Web sites were crawled by Archive-It. Web crawl information updated in finding aid annually.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: The Zamboni, 1992 -- 2021. Tufts University. Digital Collections and Archives. Medford, MA.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This series contains issues of The Zamboni, a student-run journal of humor at Tufts.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This file contains the October 7, 1992 issue and the September 20, 1994 issue of The Zamboni.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: The October 7, 1992 issue was donated by Alys Anne Wiedeke, 2019, accession UA-2019-069.

scopecontent.p: Quarterly web crawls of the Zamboni website crawled by DCA, as part of the Student Organizations web collection, to document the presesence of Tufts University student organizations on the web.
